block content
  h2.divide-section Responsive Navbar
  
  p.info Simple yet effective navbar
  
  h2 Important helpers
  p We can add class <code>.fixed</code> to make it fix in current position.
  p 
  | Also we can add class <code> .top</code> to make it fix at top. 
  | This class won't work without <code>.fixed</code> class.
  p Always add <code>.fixed</code> and <code>.top</code> class to <code>nav</code> element only.
  
  h2 Javascript 
  p We need to initialize nav. No support for data attributes in this version.

  pre
    code $(".flexnav").flexNav();


